data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. *HUGE PRICE IMPROVEMENT - SELLER IS MOTIVATED* Completely updated and move in ready, this gorgeous WATERFRONT POOL HOME boasts a ton of recent upgrades for you to enjoy ! This 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom pool home is situated on multiple lots with a total of over 1/2 an acre of land all on a freshwater canal. Enjoy your pool in complete privacy with no neighbors to your left and an expansive canal behind. The home itself features a metal roof, new tile throughout, completely renovated Master and guest bathrooms, large format tile in the showers, stylish ceiling fans, a new water filtration system, and much more ! In the kitchen there are new cabinets, granite countertops, and new/updated stainless steel appliances. The fenced in back yard is perfect for pets while also keeping the spectacular view uninhibited. Schedule your personal tour of 5839 Battersea Avenue today !
